Basic Task Structure:
    mandatory
        - id
        - description
        - status
            - not_started
            - in_progress
            - completed
    optional
        - deadline
        - current duration
            - how long you've since started the task
            - only works if task is in progress
            - in days and hours
        - priority
        - grouping


task manager:
    - changes status
    - get all tasks
    - get info on specific task
        -
    -